verbose_text: As shown in XREF_FIG, H/SD treatment (H/SD, 0.322 +/-0.043; EGFP-Adv + H/SD, 0.389 +/-0.053) decreased p-GSK3beta expression compared with in the control (0.752 +/-0.062; P < 0.05), EGFP-Adv (0.829 +/-0.034; P < 0.05) and EGFP-ADM groups (0.708 +/-0.035; P < 0.05), whereas the expression levels of inactivated p-GSK3beta were significantly enhanced in the EGFP-ADM + H/SD group (0.732 +/-0.042) compared with in the H/SD group (P < 0.05).
